data.description: Welcome home! Only 3 years young, this beautiful ranch home boasts a spacious private yard of 1.58 ACRES located in a cul de sac. With no HOA! Cobb Walk is a desirable neighborhood conveniently located to downtown Royston and mins from shops and dinning. Inside features an open floor plan with a HUGE living room and kitchen. Lots of windows providing natural light, 4 large bedrooms, 3 FULL bathrooms and a mud room. This home has everything you’re looking for! Schedule your showing today!
